vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>\u0906\u092a \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 Fast delivery \u0915\u093e \u0915\u093f\u0924\u0928\u093e Charge \u0915\u0930\u0928\u093e \u091a\u093e\u0939\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u0906\u092a \u092f\u0939\u093e show \u0915\u0930 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964  Example \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f \u092e\u0941\u091d\u0947 60 Minutes \u092e\u0947\u0902 delivery \u0926\u0947\u0928\u0947 \u0915\u093e Charge 40 Rupee \u0932\u094b\u0902\u0917\u093e\u0964 <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"160\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-24-at-12.20.38_84ff3886-1024x160.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12130 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-24-at-12.20.38_84ff3886-1024x160.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-24-at-12.20.38_84ff3886-500x78.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-24-at-12.20.38_84ff3886-768x120.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-24-at-12.20.38_84ff3886.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>Amount Type \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0906\u092a Products \u0915\u0947 \u092e\u094b\u0924\u092c\u093f\u0915 Charge \u0915\u0930 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u0906\u092a 40 \u0930\u0942\u092a\u0940 \u0915\u093e Flat \u0926\u0947-\u0926\u0947 \u092f\u093e Price \u0915\u0947 \u092e\u094b\u0924\u092c\u093f\u0915 40% discount \u092d\u0940 \u0926\u0947 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-colu